put him in the back of your truck?

07:46.711 --> 07:48.371
Your daughter's there,
for Christ's sakes.

07:48.374 --> 07:49.979
Exactly. I don't want
her thinking McCulloughs

07:49.981 --> 07:51.647
are the kind of people
who drive by a dead man

07:51.649 --> 07:53.115
and leave him hangin' in the sun.

08:05.163 --> 08:07.196
C'mon, darlin'.

08:07.231 --> 08:09.965
Come on, now.

08:10.001 --> 08:11.467
Leave that.

08:11.502 --> 08:12.331
Let's go.

08:12.334 --> 08:14.603
You can keep your granddad company.

08:22.648 --> 08:24.114
Endive.

08:24.150 --> 08:25.783
Mm-hmm.

08:31.490 --> 08:33.090
Mexican hat.

08:33.125 --> 08:34.857
Good girl.

08:34.894 --> 08:36.592
You're giving me easy ones.

09:04.690 --> 09:08.158
You wanna know what's
happening, don't you?

09:08.194 --> 09:10.694
I know you're not gonna tell me.

09:19.133 --> 09:20.504
Indian blanket.

09:20.507 --> 09:21.472
Good girl.

09:27.613 --> 09:29.513
You missed a spot.

09:29.548 --> 09:31.148
Who do you figure for it?

09:31.183 --> 09:33.750
Well, hell, Pete, I dunno.

09:33.786 --> 09:35.319
Though there is a revolution goin' on

09:35.354 --> 09:37.754
the other side of
that border over there.

09:37.790 --> 09:38.989
And our county does harbor

09:39.024 --> 09:41.292
every type of cattle thief known to man.

09:41.325 --> 09:43.792
Then we got the trigger-happy Rangers,

09:43.828 --> 09:46.262
a sheriff who can't tell his
ass from a hole in the ground,

09:46.297 --> 09:48.397
and a whole collection of
yahoos who go for a rope

09:48.432 --> 09:50.799
every time a Mexican
looks at a white lady.

09:50.835 --> 09:54.670
So I dunno, son.

09:54.705 --> 09:56.982
It's a pretty short list of suspects.

09:56.985 --> 09:58.274
Well, I got a pretty good idea

09:58.309 --> 10:00.142
which yahoo I'm gonna go see first.

